<% if @account_already_exists %>
<p> A plan already exists for this Grinnellian. Please check the username you are trying to register with. If you have forgotten your password, please use the password reset utility. </p>
<%end%>

<% if @account_exists_but_not_confirmed %>
<p> A confirmation email has already been sent to this account. Would you like to send another notification email? </p>
<%end%>

<% if @confirmation_email_sent %>
<p>An email with your activation link was just sent to <%=@user_email%>. Please check your email and navigate to the activation link.<br/>
Normally this email should be delivered instantaneously; however if you did not receive an activation email, please contact a plans admin at grinnellplans@gmail.com.</p>
<%end%>
